__e: Like, "You're ugly, and I know it for a fact, 'cause I got the evidence right there."
Until you come face-to-face with something ugly and you need me to make it go away.
Now I've got to go back to an ugly place, and if I don't, I'll be running for the rest of my life, and you and your mommy will be running with me.
